#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:19
msgid "Welcome to our new website!"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:19
msgid "We're adjusting our system to make our services available in this space."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:27
msgid "CuReMAIn"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:27
msgid "(Customer Relationship Maganer with AI)"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:30
msgid ""
"Your company's relationship with its customers is the foundation for new "
"business and maintaining its presence in today's competitive market."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:30
msgid ""
"With our AI-powered customer tracking system, this task, which requires "
"highly skilled personnel, can be optimized by using intelligent queries "
"to your databases and product documentation."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:39
msgid "RAGA"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:39
msgid "(Retrieval-Augmented Generation Agent)"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:42
msgid "We develop custom agents to automatically respond to your customers."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:42
msgid ""
"Based on a database, we can develop an agent that answers specific "
"questions collected from previous experiences with the CuReMAIn system or"
" from a product manual manufactured by the company."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:53
msgid "CybSeS"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:53
msgid "(Cyber Security Supremacy)"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:56
msgid ""
"Cybersecurity has entered a new era in 2025, where artificial "
"intelligence can be used as a shield, but unfortunately, it is also used "
"as a sword on a digital battlefield that is becoming increasingly "
"sophisticated every day."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:56
msgid ""
"We have the expertise and tools to ensure the security of your data in "
"this new battleground."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:65
msgid "ConSISO"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:65
msgid "(Consulting for ISO)"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:68
msgid "Consulting for the implementation of ISO 27001 and 42001 standards."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:68
msgid ""
"Preparing a company for ISO certification requires preparing a series of "
"documents, planning various control procedures, and checking their "
"effectiveness."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:68
msgid ""
"We have a qualified technical team to provide the necessary consultancy "
"to achieve success in first or second-party certification."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:77
msgid "TOPS"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:77
msgid "(Total On Premisses Support)"
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:80
msgid "Consulting for implementing your company's IT infrastructure."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:80
msgid ""
"Even if you use our Cloud solutions, you still need a network of "
"computers installed in your company for your employees to perform their "
"tasks."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:80
msgid ""
"We provide consulting for this implementation, from the basics, such as "
"providing quality electrical power, which is the minimum required for all"
" systems to function properly. Even migrate and use your systems in the "
"cloud."
msgstr ""

#: edcat_root/pages/templates/index.html:80
msgid ""
"If you're like some of our clients who insist on keeping your entire "
"infrastructure offline, don't worry, we have solutions for you too."
msgstr ""

